ADVANCED CERAMIC said unconsolidated sales
in June fell 4.45% to NT$100,330,000 from NT$105,007,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  6/2012           6/2011
Sales            100,330          105,007    
YOY%              -4.45%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales            560,729          577,476    
YOY%              -2.90% 
=================================================================
 